Build a **Web-Based 3D Architectural Blueprint Viewer** using **React.js, Three.js (React Three Fiber), Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB**.

The application should allow users to upload 2D architectural floor plans (PNG, JPG, PDF, or DXF files) and visualize them as interactive 3D building models directly in the browser.

### User Authentication

* User Registration and Login
* JWT Authentication
* Secure Password Hashing
* User Profile Management

### Dashboard

* Create New Project
* Upload Blueprint Files
* View Saved Projects
* Edit Existing Projects
* Delete Projects
* Search and Filter Projects

### 2D to 3D Blueprint Conversion

* Upload floor plan images or CAD files
* Detect walls, rooms, doors, and windows
* Generate 3D walls through extrusion
* Create room layouts automatically
* Generate building structure in real time

### 3D Visualization Module

* Interactive 3D Viewer using Three.js
* Rotate, Zoom, and Pan Controls
* Fullscreen Mode
* Responsive Design for Desktop and Mobile
* Smooth Rendering and Navigation

### Walkthrough Mode

* First-Person Navigation
* WASD Keyboard Controls
* Mouse Look Controls
* Collision Detection with Walls
* Realistic Movement Speed

### Layer Management

* Structural Layer
* Furniture Layer
* Electrical Layer
* Plumbing Layer
* Ceiling Layer
* Toggle Visibility for Each Layer

### Measurement Tools

* Distance Measurement Between Two Points
* Room Area Calculation
* Wall Length Calculation
* Dimension Labels

### Annotation System

* Add Notes Anywhere on the Model
* Comment Pins
* Edit/Delete Annotations
* Save Annotations to Database

### Material and Lighting Customization

* Change Wall Colors
* Apply Floor Textures
* Apply Ceiling Textures
* Furniture Materials
* Dynamic Sunlight Simulation
* Day and Night Mode
* Realistic Shadows and Reflections

### Admin Panel

* Manage Users
* Manage Projects
* View Analytics Dashboard
* Monitor Uploaded Files
* Delete Inappropriate Content

### Database Design

Collections:

* Users
* Projects
* Blueprints
* Annotations
* Materials
* Activity Logs

### Backend APIs

* Authentication APIs
* Project CRUD APIs
* File Upload APIs
* Annotation APIs
* Material Update APIs
* Admin APIs

### Additional Features

* Project Sharing via Link
* Export 3D Model as OBJ/GLTF
* Export Screenshots
* Undo/Redo Actions
* Auto Save Functionality
* Dark/Light Theme

### Technology Stack

Frontend:

* React.js
* Tailwind CSS
* React Three Fiber
* Drei
* Axios

Backend:

* Node.js
* Express.js

Database:

* MongoDB

Authentication:

* JWT
* bcrypt

Storage:

* Multer
* Cloudinary

3D Rendering:

* Three.js
* React Three Fiber

Deployment:

* Vercel (Frontend)
* Render (Backend)
* MongoDB Atlas (Database)

### UI Requirements

Create a modern professional architecture-themed interface with:

* Responsive Dashboard
* Sidebar Navigation
* Project Cards
* Interactive 3D Canvas
* Material Customization Panel
* Measurement Toolbar
* Annotation Sidebar
* Admin Dashboard

The application should follow a clean folder structure, reusable React components, RESTful API architecture, secure authentication, and production-ready coding standards.
